      "rationale": "All three FEA codes (FDA in-house, Ansys Mechanical, DePuy Synthes implementation) operate under documented software quality assurance plans including version control, regression testing, and change management procedures consistent with ASME V&V 40 Gradation 2 requirements. Achieved level 3 reflects additional multi-team cross-verification."
    },
