      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties and geometry sourced from traceable measurements with uncertainty characterization.",
      "rationale": "Titanium alloy material properties (elastic modulus, yield strength, hardening) sourced from coupon testing of production material lots. Geometric dimensions from CMM measurements of production screws and rods. Input uncertainty propagated through Monte Carlo sampling to characterize model input contribution to total prediction uncertainty."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test samples",
