      "rationale": "Testing conducted at a single load configuration per ASTM F1717 protocol. The standard prescribes a single compression-bending test condition; therefore, the range of potential in vivo loading configurations is not fully explored. This factor is below required level and represents a documented limitation acknowledged in the submission."
    },
